---
title: TheCocktailDB API — Aufrufsequenz
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Nutzer
    participant Elm as Elm (update)
    participant Api as Api.elm
    participant DB as TheCocktailDB

    Nutzer->>Elm: Glossar öffnen
    Elm->>Api: fetchCategories
    Api->>DB: GET /list.php?c=list
    DB-->>Api: ["Cocktail","Beer","Shot",...]
    Api-->>Elm: GotCategories (Ok [...])

    Nutzer->>Elm: Kategorie wählen
    Elm->>Api: fetchCocktailsByCategory "Cocktail"
    Api->>DB: GET /filter.php?c=Cocktail
    DB-->>Api: [{idDrink, strDrink, strDrinkThumb},...]
    Api-->>Elm: GotCocktailSummaries "Cocktail" (Ok [...])

    Nutzer->>Elm: Cocktail wählen
    Elm->>Api: fetchCocktailById "11007"
    Api->>DB: GET /lookup.php?i=11007
    DB-->>Api: FullCocktail (name,ingredients,measures,instructions)
    Api-->>Elm: GotFullCocktail (Ok cocktail)

    Note over Elm,DB: Suche nach Name (Glossar + Event-Suche)
    Nutzer->>Elm: Name eingeben + suchen
    Elm->>Api: searchCocktailsByName "margar"
    Api->>DB: GET /search.php?s=margar
    DB-->>Api: [FullCocktail,...]
    Api-->>Elm: GotGlossarSearchResults (Ok [...])
